    "created_at": "2015-06-29T02:29:09Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-06-29T02:29:09Z",
    "body": "The `process.cwd()` code has different behavior between launching from terminal and from `GUI`(double click icon), see\n\n```\n// Launching from terminal: <your app dirctory>/save\npath.join(process.cwd(), \"save\")\n\n// Launching from GUI: /save\npath.join(process.cwd(), \"save\")\n```\n\nSo you need to pass the `absolute` file path to make `Electron` launching from `GUI` works.\n"
